api_list.name: GET Pornstars
api_list.description:
Discover trending pornstars.
Note: gender param accepts only female, male or shemale.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://porn-pictures-api.p.rapidapi.com/pornstars/female/1"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "porn-pictures-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
